---
layout: base.njk
fullModeOnly: true
title: Evidence Dashboard
description: "Public anonymised evidence dashboard — I-PACE owner data on battery health and registered vehicles."
---

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Public Evidence</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">Evidence Dashboard</h1>
    <p class="page-header__subtitle">Anonymised aggregate data submitted voluntarily by I-PACE owners.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section section--sm" data-public-stats>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="callout callout--info" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
      <span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">ℹ️</span>
      <div class="callout__content">
        <p class="callout__title">Live owner-submitted data</p>
        <p>These figures are generated from collected vehicle and battery State of Health records. Metrics that the current forms do not collect are not shown.</p>
        <p class="text-muted" data-public-generated-at data-public-stats-status style="margin-bottom:0;">Loading latest update time...</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout callout--warning" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
      <span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
      <div class="callout__content">
        <p class="callout__title">Data disclaimer</p>
        <p>Data is submitted voluntarily and may be self-reported. Public figures are anonymised and aggregated, and sample bias may apply. Only records with consent for anonymised analysis are included.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0;"><a href="/methodology/">Read the methodology</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">Summary statistics</h2>
    <div class="grid grid--3" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value" data-public-stat="ownersContributed">Loading</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Owners contributed data</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Distinct contributors with registered cars</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value" data-public-stat="vehiclesRegistered">Loading</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Cars registered</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Included in public aggregates</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value" data-public-stat="averageReportedSoh" data-public-stat-format="percent">Loading</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Average latest reported SoH</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">One latest reading per car</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value" data-public-stat="sohReadings">Loading</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">SoH readings collected</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">All eligible measurements</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value" data-public-stat="vehiclesWithRepeatSoh">Loading</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Cars with repeat SoH readings</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Available for degradation analysis</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value" data-public-stat="averageSohChange" data-public-stat-format="change">Loading</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Average reported SoH change</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">First to latest repeat reading</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">Collected distributions</h2>
    <div class="grid" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
      <div class="chart-panel">
        <h3 class="chart-panel__title">Latest State of Health by car</h3>
        <div class="bar-chart" data-public-distribution="soh" aria-live="polite">
          <p class="text-muted">Loading collected data...</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-panel">
        <h3 class="chart-panel__title">Registered cars by model year</h3>
        <div class="bar-chart" data-public-distribution="model-year" aria-live="polite">
          <p class="text-muted">Loading collected data...</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <noscript><p class="callout callout--warning">JavaScript is required to load the latest aggregate statistics.</p></noscript>

    <div class="callout callout--success">
      <span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">📊</span>
      <div class="callout__content">
        <p class="callout__title">Strengthen the evidence</p>
        <p>Register your I-PACE and add new SoH measurements over time. Repeat readings help quantify battery degradation.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0;"><a href="/member/submit-vehicle-data/">Register a car</a> or <a href="/member/dashboard/">update an existing car's SoH</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
